{"tid":633526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國CIA局長密會金正恩　商談美朝領導人會議","createTime":"2018-04-18T11:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T13:40:28.000Z","uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fa415335cf3085908cff36bf31825e4c0e319550","tid":633526,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:38:16.000Z","msg":"根據《華盛頓郵報》（Washington Post）17日報導，美國候任國務卿、現任中情局局長蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）在復活節的周末（3月30至4月1日左右）訪問北韓，曾與北韓領導人金正恩見面。當時金正恩才結束訪問中國、與中國國家主席習近平見面後不久。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國、北韓計劃在月底或6月初舉行領導人會面，但會議相關細節至今尚未公布。蓬佩奧與金正恩見面是為協調美國、北韓領導人會議細節。美國總統川普（Donald Trump）已經聽取蓬佩奧報告密訪北韓細節，相信美國、北韓領導人會議談判有用。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n根據《路透》、《香港01》報導，川普於佛州私人別墅接見正在美國訪問的日本首相安倍晉三。川普在記者會上表示：「美國與北韓展開非常高級別的直接對談。」川普這段談話所指的美國非常高級別代表人物就是蓬佩奧，先前一度有媒體誤會，川普與金正恩已經直接對話。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《美國有線新聞網》（CNN）18日報導，目前最有可能舉辦美國、北韓領導人會議的地點包括蒙古國首都烏蘭巴托、兩韓非軍事區、瑞典首都德哥爾摩、瑞士城市日內瓦、新加坡、馬來西亞、甚至首爾及平壤。不過，但目前美國、北韓尚未做出會議地點決議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=39040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D39040&d=ee90mIes5nct%2B2vf3A%2FOTpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d38363d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=39040</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2018/04/17/politics/mike-pompeo-kim-jong-un-visit/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2Fpolitics%2Fmike-pompeo-kim-jong-un-visit%2Findex.html&d=ee90mIes5nct%2B2vf3A%2FOTpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=15ef92f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2Fpolitics%2Fmike-pompeo-kim-jong-un-visit%2Findex.html&h=8aac93a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2018/04/17/politics/mike-pompeo-kim-jong-un-visit/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n侵侵又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bfda31806b406fb47cc605449207c2399f8656","tid":633526,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53e950e7a9d007e82a73566dd3a8cd537cd439c","tid":633526,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"Donald J. Trump<br />\n&rlm;<br />\nVerified account<br />\n <br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n 1h1 hour ago<br />\nMore<br />\nMike Pompeo met with Kim Jong Un in North Korea last week. Meeting went very smoothly and a good relationship was formed. Details of Summit are being worked out now. Denuclearization will be a great thing for World, but also for North Korea!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/986555533535731712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F986555533535731712&d=ee90mIes5nct%2B2vf3A%2FOTpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=616b1e86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F986555533535731712&h=bb7e2f8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/986555533535731712</a><br />\n<br />\n堅野黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037f54674d82f00c9a0b40b858762107f29f570f","tid":633526,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"16c4c0185eeca101f9bcc74cf5e483128007d198","tid":633526,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}